style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'> </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Client has purchased or will
purchase Apple hardware (“Client Hardware”) directly from Apple Inc. or its <span
class=SpellE>authorised</span> resellers (“Apple”). Legal and beneficial title
to Client Hardware passes directly from Apple to Client upon dispatch/delivery;
<span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> never acquires title, ownership, security
interest, or possessory lien in Client Hardware.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:28.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;
