style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
class=SpellE><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Sentimento</span></span><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> provides Configuration Services to
install software on Client Hardware while held as bailee for reward.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:28.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-14.15pt;line-height:110%;mso-list:
l44 level1 lfo25'><![if !supportLists]><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'>C.<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Client engages <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
as limited agent solely for Delivery Acceptance and as bailee for Configuration
Services, on the terms set out below.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>NOW
IT IS AGREED</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> as
follows:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>CLAUSE
1: DEFINITIONS AND INTERPRETATION</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>1.1
Definitions</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>In
this Agreement, unless the context otherwise requires:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“<b><span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Business Day</span>”</b> means a day (other than Saturday, Sunday
or public holiday) on which banks are open for general business in <span
class=GramE>Hong Kong;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“Bundle”
</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>means the Triple
Pack, Complete Regular Suite, or Ultimate Bundle pricing tiers set out in
Schedule D.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“<span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Client Account</span>”</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>
means the administrative account created on Client Hardware for operation of
the Open Claw agent, comprising a username provided by Client and an initial
password generated by <span class=SpellE><span class=GramE>Sentimento</span></span><span
class=GramE>;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“<span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Client Hardware</span>”</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>
means the Apple hardware (Mac Mini, iMac, or other specified model) purchased
by Client directly from Apple, identified by serial number(s) set out in the
applicable Order <span class=GramE>Form;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“Coding
Models”</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> means the
specialized code-generation LLMs listed in Schedule D, Section 1.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“<span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Configuration Fee</span>” </span></b><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'>means the fees payable for Configuration Services as
set out in the Order <span class=GramE>Form;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“<span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Configuration Period</span>” </span></b><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'>means the period commencing upon <span class=SpellE>Sentimento’s</span>
acceptance of delivery of Client Hardware and ending upon delivery of
configured Client Hardware to the carrier for shipment to Client (or upon
termination pursuant to Clause 9<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“<span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Configuration Services</span>”</span></b><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'> means: (a) installation of the Open Claw base agent;
(b) installation of selected Vertical Modules per Schedule B (if the Gatekeeper
Protocol conditions are satisfied); (c) creation of Client Account; (d)
application of the <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> Seal; and (e)
diagnostic <span class=GramE>testing;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“Dashboard”
</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>means the secure
client portal hosted at www.monoclaw.app accessible exclusively via Google
Single Sign-On (SSO) authentication per Schedule E, serving as the sole and
exclusive method for all notices, billing communications, order tracking, and
official correspondence between the parties.<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“<span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Data Subject</span>”</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>
has the meaning given in the <span class=GramE>PDPO;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“<span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Delivery Acceptance</span>”</span></b><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'> means the limited authority granted to <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> under Clause 2 and Schedule <span class=GramE>A;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“Deployment
Fee” </span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>means the fee
payable for the technical service of downloading, quantizing (if applicable),
and integrating a Local Model into the Open Claw environment.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“<span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Disposal Ordinance</span>” </span></b><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'>means the Disposal of Uncollected Goods Ordinance
(Cap. 150<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“<span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>DPA</span>”</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>
means the Data Processing Agreement set out in Schedule <span class=GramE>C;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“Final
Payment Due Date:</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>
means the date falling seven (7) calendar days after Client’s receipt of the
configured Client Hardware, by which the remaining sixty percent (60%) of the
Configuration Fee must be paid pursuant to Clause 12.4(c).<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“<span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Force Majeure</span>”</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>
means any event beyond the reasonable control of the affected party, including
but not limited to acts of God, war, terrorism, strikes, failure of third-party
telecommunications, pandemic restrictions under the Prevention and Control of
Disease Ordinance (Cap. 599), or supply chain failures by <span class=GramE>Apple;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“<span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Gatekeeper Protocol</span>”</span></b><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'> means the verification procedure set out in Clause
4.6 for Tier 1 <span class=GramE>Tools;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
