inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>(c) <b>Non-Repudiation</b>: Client shall not dispute the
validity of the Agreement on the basis that the signature was electronic,
applied via web interface, or stored digitally, provided the audit trail
indicates successful completion of the steps in Clause 1.3(a).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>CLAUSE
2: LIMITED AGENCY FOR DELIVERY ACCEPTANCE</span></b><b><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>2.1
Appointment and Scope</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Client
hereby appoints <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> as its limited agent
solely for Delivery Acceptance strictly subject to the limitations in Clause
2.2. This agency relationship terminates automatically upon <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
transferring possession of configured Client Hardware to the carrier for
shipment to Client.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Client
grants this limited agency as a standing authority for all Client Hardware
ordered during the term of this <span class=GramE>Agreement, and</span>
executes Schedule A by signing the Master Agreement</span></i><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>2.2
Strict Limitations on Authority</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span class=SpellE><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'>Sentimento’s</span></span><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'> authority as agent is strictly limited to:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
executing proof of delivery receipts, waybills, and carrier release forms on
Client’s behalf, provided such documents identify the recipient as “<span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> Ltd as agent for [Client Name]<span class=GramE>”;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
inspecting external packaging of Client Hardware for visible transit damage and
noting such damage on carrier’s <span class=GramE>paperwork;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(c)
logging serial numbers, IMEI numbers, and hardware specifications against
Client’s account; and<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(d)
communicating with Apple or carriers solely to report visible transit damage or
arrange delivery logistics, <span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>without authority to negotiate
remedies, waivers, or refunds</span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>2.3
Express Exclusions of Authority</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span class=SpellE><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'>Sentimento</span></span><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>
has <b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>NO authority</span></b> (whether express, implied, or apparent)
to:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
purchase Client Hardware or any goods on Client’s <span class=GramE>behalf;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
pay for Client Hardware or accept refunds, credits, or rebates from Apple using
Client’s funds or payment <span class=GramE>instruments;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(c)
negotiate, vary, or waive any terms of sale between Client and <span
class=GramE>Apple;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(d)
create any obligation binding Client beyond the specific act of accepting <span
class=GramE>delivery;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(e)
represent to any third party that <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> owns,
holds title to, or has a security interest in Client Hardware; or<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(f)
effect any change to Client’s Apple ID, iCloud account, or Apple Business
Manager enrollment.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>2.4
Title and Risk Allocation</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Title:</span></b> Legal and beneficial title to Client Hardware
passes directly from Apple to Client upon Apple’s dispatch of the Hardware to <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> (or upon Apple’s electronic acceptance of Client’s
order), and never vests in <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Risk - First Transit (Apple to <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>)</span></b><span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>:</span> Risk of loss or damage during transit from Apple to <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento’s</span> premises remains with Client (or with
Apple/carrier per Apple’s terms), except that <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
shall bear risk for loss caused by its <span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>negligent failure to inspect
and document visible external damage</span> upon delivery acceptance.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(c)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Inspection Duty</span></b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>:</span> <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
shall inspect external packaging upon delivery and, if damage is visible, <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> shall note such damage on carrier paperwork and
post a notification to the Dashboard within 4 Business Hours of delivery <span
class=GramE>acceptance..</span> Failure to document visible external damage
constitutes negligence for the purposes of Clause 2.4(b).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(d)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>No Implied Warranty</span></b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>:</span> <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
makes no warranty regarding Apple’s delivery performance and shall not be
liable for Apple’s shipping delays or errors.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(e)
<b>Evidentiary Standard</b>: Clause 2.4(c) provides the evidentiary standard
for the exception in 2.4(b)<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>CLAUSE
3: BAILMENT</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>3.1
Bailment Relationship</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Upon
accepting delivery, <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> holds Client Hardware
as <span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>bailee for reward</span> during the Configuration Period. Client
retains full ownership as bailor. This bailment is solely for the purpose of
performing Configuration Services and not for any other purpose.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>3.2
Duty of Care</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
Standard: <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> owes a duty of reasonable care
(not strict liability or insurance liability) for the safekeeping of Client
Hardware, commensurate with the standard expected of a professional technology
services provider exercising reasonable skill and care.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
Specific Obligations: Without limiting Clause 3.2(a), <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
shall:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:28.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;
