</span>ii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Selected Vertical Modules (subject
to Gatekeeper Protocol in Clause 4.6<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:28.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;
