style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Current practicing certificate
under the Legal Practitioners Ordinance (Cap. 159), Medical Registration
Ordinance (Cap. 161), Professional Accountants Ordinance (Cap. 50), or
Immigration Service Providers Ordinance (Cap. 115) (as applicable<span
class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
