</span>ii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Certificate of currency for
professional indemnity insurance with minimum coverage of HKD $1,000,000 (or as
specified by the relevant professional body<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
