</span>iii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Written confirmation that <span
class=GramE>use</span> of the Tools will be supervised by the certified
professional named in (<span class=SpellE>i</span>) if the actual user is a
trainee or support staff;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Specific Undertaking</span></b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>:</span> Client shall execute
the specific undertaking at Schedule B, Section <span class=GramE>3.5;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(c)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Verification</span></b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>:</span> <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
shall retain copies of the documents in (a) for the duration of the Agreement
plus 6 years.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(d)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Consequence of Non-Compliance</span></b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>:</span> If <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
installs Tier 1 Tools without obtaining the documentation in (a) and (b), <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> shall be liable for any claims arising from
unauthorized practice of profession by Client, <span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>notwithstanding the liability
cap in Clause 8.1</span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>This
Gatekeeper Protocol applies equally to Local Models where such models are
designated as “Restricted” in Schedule D (if any), requiring verification of
Client’s intended use case for models subject to export control or specialized
use restrictions.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

