<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Carrier Selection</span></b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>:</span> <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
shall use a reputable courier with tracking and insurance (e.g., SF Express,
FedEx, DHL) for return shipment.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Risk Transfer</span></b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>:</span> Risk of loss or damage
to Client Hardware passes from <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> to Client
upon delivery of the sealed package to the carrier for return shipment, <span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>unless</span> loss/damage is caused by <span class=SpellE>Sentimento’s</span>
negligent packing (evidenced by photographic records).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(c)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Insurance</span></b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>:</span> <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
shall procure transit insurance for the return shipment as bailee (or ensure
Client’s insurance covers transit).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

