<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>9.1
Term</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>This
Agreement commences on the date of execution and continues until completion of
Configuration Services and delivery of Client Hardware, unless terminated
earlier in accordance with this Clause.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>9.2
Termination by Client</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Client
may terminate immediately by written notice. If Configuration is complete, all
Configuration Fees remain due. If Configuration is incomplete, Client shall pay
pro-rata fees for work completed and costs incurred (including non-refundable
software <span class=SpellE>licence</span> fees paid by <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>9.3
Termination by <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span></span></b><b><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span class=SpellE><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'>Sentimento</span></span><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>
may terminate by written notice if:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
Client fails to pay the Deposit (forty percent (40%)) required by Clause
12.4(b) upon execution of the Order <span class=GramE>Form;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
Client fails to pay the final sixty percent (60%) of the Configuration Fee
within <b>fourteen (14) calendar days</b> following the Final Payment Due Date
specified in Clause <span class=GramE>12.4(c);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(c)
Client breaches the Gatekeeper Protocol conditions (Clause 4.6); or<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(d)
Client provides false information regarding professional status.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Upon
termination, <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> must return Client Hardware
(in its then condition) within 5 Business Days, notwithstanding Clause 3.3 (no
lien). <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> may claim storage fees at HKD $500
per day after termination if Client fails to collect Hardware.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>9.4
<span class=GramE>Post-Termination</span></span></b><b><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Software <span class=SpellE>Licences</span></span></b><span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>:</span> <span class=SpellE>Licences</span> granted in Clause 5
and Schedule B survive termination and are perpetual as to the specific Client
Hardware.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Data Deletion</span></b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>:</span> <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
shall delete <span class=SpellE>Supabase</span> data within 30 days per Clause
6.4.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(c)
<b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Survival</span></b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>:</span> Clauses 1, 4.5, 5, 6,
8, 10, and 11 survive termination.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(d)
<b>Local Model Survival</b>: Client’s <span class=SpellE>licence</span> to use
Local Models (deriving from Upstream Licensors) survives termination of this
Agreement. <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> has no technical ability to
terminate or remotely disable Local Models post-deployment, regardless of
termination of this Agreement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

