border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>10.3
Duration</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Confidentiality
obligations survive termination for <b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>3 years</span> </b>(or
perpetually for trade secrets).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

