border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>CLAUSE
11: GENERAL PROVISIONS</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>11.1
Entire Agreement</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>This
<b>Agreement (including Schedules A, B, C, D, and E)</b> constitutes the entire
agreement between parties and supersedes prior negotiations, representations,
or warranties. No representation, warranty, or inducement not expressly set
forth herein is binding.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>11.2
No Partnership or Agency</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Nothing
in this Agreement creates a partnership, joint venture, or general agency
relationship. <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> acts only as bailee and
limited agent for Delivery Acceptance as specifically defined. Client has no
authority to bind <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>11.3
Assignment</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
Client may not assign this Agreement without <span class=SpellE>Sentimento’s</span>
prior written consent (not unreasonably withheld).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
<span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> may assign to affiliates or successors in
connection with a merger or sale of assets, provided the assignee agrees to be
bound.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>11.4
Set-Off</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>All
sums payable under this Agreement shall be paid in full without set-off,
counterclaim, deduction, or withholding (except as required by law).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>11.5
Severability and Waiver</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>If
any provision is held invalid or unenforceable, it shall be modified to the
minimum extent necessary to make it valid, or if not possible, severed without
affecting the remaining provisions. No waiver of any breach shall constitute a
waiver of any other breach.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>To
the extent permitted by law, the parties irrevocably waive any right to a trial
by jury in any legal proceeding arising out of or relating to this Agreement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>11.6
Notices</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>(a)
<b>Exclusive Notification Platform</b>: All notices, demands, or other
communications under this Agreement shall be given exclusively via the
Dashboard. Email, postal mail, SMS, or telephone shall not constitute valid
notice unless expressly required by mandatory applicable law.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>(b)
<b>Deemed Receipt</b>: Any notification posted to the Dashboard shall be deemed
received: <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:28.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;
