<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>(c)
<b>Client Duty to Monitor</b>: Client shall check the Dashboard at least once
every Business Day during the Configuration Period, and at least once per
calendar week thereafter. Failure to monitor the Dashboard shall not excuse any
obligation, deadline, or liability under this Agreement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>(d)
<b>Statutory Override</b>: If any Hong Kong statute or regulation mandatorily
requires a specific notification method (e.g., registered post for termination
under specific consumer protection laws), such statutory method shall prevail
solely for that specific notice, but Dashboard notification shall remain valid
for all contractual purposes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>11.7
Governing Law and Jurisdiction</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
This Agreement shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws
of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
The parties submit to the non-exclusive jurisdiction of the Hong Kong courts
for interim injunctive relief, and to the exclusive jurisdiction of HKIAC
arbitration (Clause 11.8) for all other disputes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>11.8
Dispute Resolution</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Any
dispute shall be referred to arbitration administered by the Hong Kong
International Arbitration Centre (“HKIAC”) under the UNCITRAL Arbitration
Rules:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
Seat: <span class=GramE>Hong Kong;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
Tribunal: One arbitrator appointed per HKIAC <span class=GramE>procedures;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(c)
Language: <span class=GramE>English;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(d)
Confidentiality: Proceedings and awards are confidential.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>11.9
Further Assurances<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Each
party shall execute and deliver such further documents and take such further
actions as may be reasonably necessary to give effect to the provisions of this
Agreement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>11.10
Platform Availability &amp; Risk Allocation<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
<b>Dependency on Google SSO</b>: Client acknowledges that Dashboard access is
exclusively dependent on Google LLC’s authentication services (Schedule E). <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> shall not be liable for any failure to notify
resulting from Google SSO outages, Client’s loss of Google account access, or
Client’s failure to maintain a valid Google account.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
<b>Backup Access Protocol</b>: If Dashboard access is unavailable due to Force
Majeure affecting Google (Clause 13.4), <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
may, at its sole discretion, utilize the last known email address on file for
urgent matters only (termination, security breaches), provided such alternative
method does not constitute a waiver of Clause 11.6(a).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(c)
<b>Monthly Archives</b>: As a supplementary record-keeping measure, <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> shall make available a downloadable PDF archive
of all Dashboard notifications for the preceding calendar month, accessible via
the Dashboard for Client’s offline records.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>11.11
Dashboard Records<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>&quot;<span
class=SpellE>Sentimento’s</span> system logs showing the timestamp of a
notification’s posting to Client’s Dashboard shall constitute conclusive
evidence of the notification’s dispatch and receipt for the purposes of this
Agreement and any dispute resolution proceedings.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>11.12
Client Duty to Retain<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“Client
acknowledges that while <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> retains signed
contracts for 7 years, Client shall also download and retain a copy of the
executed Agreement from the Dashboard within 48 hours of countersignature.
Client’s failure to do so shall not excuse performance of obligations under the
Agreement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;line-height:110%'><b><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>CLAUSE 12: FEES AND PAYMENT<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

