inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>12.1 Configuration Fee<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>The base Configuration Fee for the Services described in
Clause 4 is fixed at <b>Hong Kong Dollars Thirty-Nine Thousand Nine Hundred and
Ninety-Nine (HKD $39,999.00)</b> per unit of Client Hardware (inclusive of
shipping costs).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
