to settle the Configuration Fee via Stripe in one of the following currencies:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>(a) Hong Kong Dollars (HKD<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>(b) United States Dollars (USD<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>(c) Chinese Renminbi (CNY<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>(d) Euros (EUR); or<o:p></o:p></span></p>

