letter-spacing:.4pt'>12.4 Payment Schedule and Method<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>(a) <b>Hardware Procurement<o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>Client shall purchase the Client Hardware directly from
Apple Inc. via the online store link provided on <span class=SpellE>MonoClaw’s</span>
website. <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> shall at no time receive, hold,
or process funds for the purchase of hardware, and <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
makes no representation regarding Apple’s pricing, availability, or delivery
timelines. Title to the hardware passes directly from Apple to Client as
specified in Clause 2.4(a).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>(b) <b>Service Fee Deposit (40%) -- Conditional upon
Execution</b><o:p></o:p></span></p>

