</span>iii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><b><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Reminder
Protocol</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:
.4pt'>: Upon execution of the Agreement via the Native Signing System, <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> shall post an immediate confirmation to the
Dashboard containing credentials (if first-time user) and instructions for
completing the Hardware Order Details. <b>If Client fails to complete the
Hardware Order Details within the 24-hour window, <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
shall post a notification to the Dashboard</b> alerting Client to the
deficiency. Non-receipt of such reminders due to Client’s failure to monitor
the Dashboard shall not excuse Client’s obligation under this Clause 12.4(g).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>(h) <b>Hardware Delivery Failure<o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>If Client Hardware is not physically received by <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> within <b>fourteen (14)</b> <b>days</b> of the
Apple estimated delivery date (as recorded in the Dashboard pursuant to Clause
12.4(g)), <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> may terminate this Agreement and
retain the Deposit as liquidated damages for reserved configuration capacity,
unless Client has notified <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> via the
Dashboard of Apple shipping delays or Force Majeure applies.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>12.5 Confidentiality of Hardware Delivery Address<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>(a) <b>Provision of Address<o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span class=SpellE><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Sentimento</span></span><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'> shall provide
Client with a designated receiving address (the “<span class=SpellE><b>Sentimento</b></span><b>
Receiving Address</b>”) via the secure Client Dashboard, formatted specifically
for entry into Apple’s online store checkout system. This address is provided
solely for the purpose of the Client placing the single, specific Apple Order
under this Agreement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>(b) <b>Strict Confidentiality Obligation<o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>The <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> Receiving Address
constitutes <b>Strictly Confidential Information</b> under Clause 10. Client
acknowledges that unauthorized disclosure could compromise facility security,
facilitate fraud, result in misdirected deliveries, or disrupt <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento’s</span> operations.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>(c) <b>Absolute Prohibition on Disclosure</b><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>Client shall <b>not</b>:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

