</span>i.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Disclose,
share, publish, post on social media, transmit via unsecured email, or make
available the <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> Receiving Address to any
third party (including other potential customers, resellers, competitors, or
public forums<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

