</span>ii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Use the <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> Receiving Address for any purpose other than the
specific Apple Order under this <span class=GramE>Agreement;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
