</span>iii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Permit any
person other than Client’s authorized signatories (who are bound by
confidentiality) to view the Dashboard page displaying the address.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>(d) <b>Punitive Actions for Breach<o:p></o:p></b></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>Without prejudice to <span class=SpellE>Sentimento’s</span>
other rights under this Agreement, breach of this Clause 12.5 shall entitle <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> to:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:28.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-28.35pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-7.05pt;
line-height:110%;mso-list:l20 level1 lfo24'><![if !supportLists]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
letter-spacing:.4pt'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'><span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>i.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><b><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Immediate
Termination</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>: Terminate this Agreement immediately without refund of
any fees paid (including the non-refundable Deposit), and retain the Client
Hardware (if received) pending <span class=GramE>resolution;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:28.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;
