</span>ii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><b><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Liquidated
Damages</span></b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:
.4pt'>: Claim liquidated damages of HKD $50,000 for each instance of
unauthorized disclosure, acknowledged by Client as a genuine pre-estimate of
loss (including reputational harm, security remediation, and operational
disruption<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
