</span>iii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><b><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Indemnification</span></b><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>: Recover all
losses, costs, and expenses (including legal fees on a solicitor-client basis)
incurred by <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> arising from the breach,
including costs of intercepting unauthorized deliveries or enhancing security;
and<o:p></o:p></span></p>

