</span>ii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Epidemic or
pandemic (as declared by the World Health <span class=SpellE>Organisation</span>
or the Government of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region<span
class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:28.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-28.35pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-7.05pt;
line-height:110%;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo37'><![if !supportLists]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
letter-spacing:.4pt'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'><span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>iii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Terrorist
attack, civil war, civil commotion or riots, war, threat of or preparation for
war, armed conflict, imposition of sanctions, embargo, or breaking off of
diplomatic <span class=GramE>relations;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:28.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-28.35pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-7.05pt;
line-height:110%;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo37'><![if !supportLists]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
letter-spacing:.4pt'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'><span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>iv.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Nuclear,
chemical or biological contamination or sonic <span class=GramE>boom;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:28.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-28.35pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-7.05pt;
line-height:110%;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo37'><![if !supportLists]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
letter-spacing:.4pt'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'><span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>v.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Any law or any
action taken by a government or public authority (including without limitation
imposing an export or import restriction, quota or prohibition, or failing to
grant a necessary <span class=SpellE>licence</span> or consent for cross-border
data transfer<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:28.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-28.35pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-7.05pt;
line-height:110%;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo37'><![if !supportLists]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
letter-spacing:.4pt'><span style='mso-list:Ignore'><span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span>vi.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Collapse of
buildings, fire, explosion or accident (other than caused by <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento’s</span> negligence<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:28.35pt;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:-28.35pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-7.05pt;
