</span></span></span><![endif]><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'>Interruption or failure of utility service (including
electricity, gas, water, telecommunications<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;
