style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Supply chain
disruptions affecting Apple’s ability to manufacture or deliver the Client
Hardware to <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>; or<o:p></o:p></span></p>

