</span>i.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>If <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> has received the Client Hardware but not
completed Configuration, <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> shall return the
Hardware to Client (at <span class=SpellE>Sentimento’s</span> cost if Force
Majeure originated with <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>, otherwise at
Client’s cost<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

