</span>ii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
class=SpellE><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:
.4pt'>Sentimento</span></span><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
letter-spacing:.4pt'> shall refund to Client any Configuration Fees paid, less
reasonable costs actually incurred up to the date of termination (e.g.,
non-refundable software <span class=SpellE>licences</span>, custom components<span
class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

