</span>iii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><![endif]><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;letter-spacing:.4pt'>Clauses 8
(Liability), 10 (Confidentiality), and 13.4 shall survive termination.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

