inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>3.2
Medical/Dental Warranty</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>If
any Medical/Dental Module is selected, Client warrants that:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
Client is a registered medical practitioner under the Medical Registration
Ordinance (Cap. 161), a registered dentist under the Dentists Registration
Ordinance (Cap. 156), or supervised clinical <span class=GramE>staff;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
Client maintains registration with the Medical Council of Hong Kong or Dental
Council of Hong Kong and maintains appropriate malpractice insurance (minimum
HKD $10,000,000 for private practice<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(c)
Use of Medical Modules is limited to administrative scheduling, documentation
assistance, and patient reminders, <b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>NOT clinical diagnosis,
treatment decisions, or <span class=GramE>prescription<span style='border:none;
font-weight:normal'>;</span></span></span></b><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(d)
Client acknowledges that <span class=SpellE><b><span style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;
mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>ScribeAI</span></b></span><b><span
style='border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'> and <span class=SpellE>MedReminder</span> Bot are administrative
software only and are not “medical devices”</span></b> under the Medical Device
Administrative Control System.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

