Output from Accounting Modules constitutes calculation assistance only and
requires verification by a qualified accountant before use in financial
statements or tax filings.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
