<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-size:20.0pt;line-height:110%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>SCHEDULE C – Data Processing Agreement (DPA)</span></b><b><span
style='font-size:20.0pt;line-height:110%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>PART
OF MASTER SERVICES AND BAILMENT AGREEMENT DATED {{signed_date}}</span></b><b><span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>SECTION
1 – DEFINITIONS AND SCOPE</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>This
DPA applies where <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> processes Personal Data
on behalf of Client in connection with the creation of Client Accounts (Data
Processor services) and where <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> processes
Personal Data as Data User (Controller) for its own business purposes including
contract execution. Terms defined in the PDPO have the same meaning herein.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>SECTION
2 – ROLES</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>(a)
<b>Data User (Controller) </b>– <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>: For <b>hardware
logs, device photographs, <span class=SpellE>Sentimento’s</span> own business
records, and contract execution data</b> (including electronic signature
representations, IP addresses, device fingerprints, authentication tokens, and
audit trails generated via the Native Signing System), <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
acts as Data User under PDPO.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>(b)
<b>Data User (Controller) – Client</b>: Client is the Data User (controller) of
Personal Data provided for account creation (e.g., employee names, contact
details) and for Gatekeeper Protocol documentation (professional credentials,
insurance certificates).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>(c)
<b>Data Processor (for Client)</b>: For Client Account creation data
(usernames, encrypted passwords, account credentials, address), <span
class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> acts as Data Processor processing Personal Data
on behalf of Client. The terms of Sections 3-10 of this Schedule apply to such
processing.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>SECTION
3 – PROCESSING INSTRUCTIONS</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span class=SpellE><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'>Sentimento</span></span><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>
shall process Personal Data only:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
in accordance with Client’s documented instructions (this Agreement constitutes
such instructions<span class=GramE>);</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
to create the Client Account and transmit initial credentials to <span
class=GramE>Client;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(c)
for the duration necessary to perform Configuration Services (maximum 7 days
after account creation).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>SECTION
4 – SECURITY MEASURES</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span class=SpellE><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'>Sentimento</span></span><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>
shall implement appropriate technical and <span class=SpellE>organisational</span>
measures to protect Personal Data against <span class=SpellE>unauthorised</span>
processing, including:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(a)
Encryption of passwords using <span class=SpellE>bcrypt</span> or Argon2
hashing <span class=GramE>algorithms;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(b)
Secure transmission via TLS <span class=GramE>1.3;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(c)
Access limited to essential personnel <span class=GramE>only;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(d)
Destruction of plaintext passwords after 7 days.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>(e)
<b>For Native Signing System</b>: SHA-256 hashing of signed documents and immutable
write-once storage (WORM) for audit trails<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>SECTION
5 – SUB-PROCESSORS</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span class=SpellE><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Sentimento</span></span><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>
uses <span class=SpellE><b>Supabase</b></span><b> Inc. (US)</b> as a
sub-processor for account metadata (not passwords) and hardware diagnostic
logs. <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> does not use third-party electronic
signature platforms (e.g., DocuSign) for contract execution; all signature data
is processed natively within <span class=SpellE>Sentimento’s</span> controlled
infrastructure. <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> has executed Standard
Contractual Clauses with <span class=SpellE>Supabase</span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>SECTION
6 –DATA SUBJECT RIGHTS</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span class=SpellE><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Sentimento</span></span><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>
shall assist Client in responding to data subject access requests under PDPO,
to the extent technically feasible. For signature data processed as Data User
under Section 2(a), <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> shall respond to data
subject requests directly in accordance with PDPO requirements.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>SECTION
7 – DATA BREACH NOTIFICATION</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span class=SpellE><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif;border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;
padding:0in'>Sentimento</span></span><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>
shall post notification of any accidental or unauthorized access to Personal
Data (data breach) to the Dashboard within <b>twenty-four (24) hours </b>of
becoming aware. Client acknowledges that this satisfies immediate notification
requirements under the PDPO and accepts that actual awareness by Client’s
personnel is dependent on Dashboard monitoring compliance under Clause 11.6(c).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>SECTION
8 – RETURN &amp; DELETION</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>(a)
Upon completion of Configuration Services or termination, <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>
shall return all Personal Data processed as Processor to Client (via secure
handover of credentials) and delete all copies from its systems within 7 days,
except as required by law.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>(b)
<b>Signature Data Retention</b>: Notwithstanding Clause 8(a), contract
execution data processed under Section 2(a) (including electronic signatures
and audit trails) shall be retained by <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span> as
Data User for 7 years from the date of execution (or such longer period as
required by applicable limitation periods), after which it shall be securely
deleted or anonymized.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>SECTION
9 – AUDIT</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span class=SpellE><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'>Sentimento</span></span><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>
shall make available to Client all information necessary to demonstrate
compliance with this DPA and allow for audits by Client (with reasonable
notice, not more than once per year).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
border:none windowtext 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:none windowtext 0in;padding:0in'>SECTION
10 – LIABILITY</span></b><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span class=SpellE><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'>Sentimento’s</span></span><span style='font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'> liability for breaches of this DPA is subject to the
liability cap in Clause 8.1 of the Master Agreement, save for gross negligence
or <span class=SpellE>wilful</span> misconduct.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>ACKNOWLEDGMENT<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>By
signing the Signature Page on Pages 53 and 54 of the Master Agreement, Client
acknowledges that it has reviewed and understood this Schedule C and consents
to the processing of Personal Data as described herein, including the dual
roles of Data User and Data Processor, the security measures implemented, and
the retention periods specified (including the 7-year retention of contract
execution data). Client warrants that it has obtained all necessary consents
and provided all necessary notifications under the PDPO for the processing of
any Personal Data provided to <span class=SpellE>Sentimento</span>, including
employee data for Client Account creation and professional credentials for
Gatekeeper Protocol compliance.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<b><span style='font-size:20.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:DengXian;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'><br
clear=all style='mso-special-character:line-break;page-break-before:always'>
</span></b>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-size:20.0pt;line-height:115%;
font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-size:20.0pt;line-height:110%;font-family:
"Times New Roman",serif'>SCHEDULE D – Local Model Deployment Options<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>PART
OF MASTER SERVICES BAILMENT AGREEMENT DATED {{signed_date}}<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:center;
line-height:110%'><b><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>SECTION 1
– REGULAR MODELS (GENERAL PURPOSE)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:4.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:110%'><i><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Sorted
by Parameter Purpose<o:p></o:p></span></i></p>

